{
  "texts": [
    "The inclusion criteria for our analysis encompassed papers that focused on the application of AI technologies within the Metaverse context and explored the associated challenges.",
    "We excluded papers that primarily focused on AI outside the scope of the Metaverse or those that were not directly related to the central theme of our study.",
    "To ensure the rigor and reliability of our analysis, the screening process was conducted by multiple researchers independently.",
    "Any discrepancies or disagreements in the paper selection were resolved through discussion and consensus among the research team.",
    "This approach helped us maintain objectivity and minimize potential bias in the selection process."
  ]
}